## Skill Tags Reference

Tags determine which Link Runes can attach to a Skill Rune. A Link Rune checks if the Skill Rune's tags match its requirements.

| Tag | Meaning |
|---|---|
| Attack | Scales with attack stats; weapon damage based |
| Spell | Scales with spell stats; cast-based |
| Melee | Hits within melee range |
| Projectile | Fires a projectile |
| AoE (Area of Effect) | Hits a zone |
| Strike | Single hit or discrete hits (vs DoT) |
| DoT | Damage over time effect |
| Channel | Sustained channeled skill |
| Duration | Skill has a timed duration |
| Toggle | Persistent on/off mode; costs resource while active |
| Movement | Moves the player character |
| Physical / Fire / Cold / Lightning / Poison | Damage element type |
| Bow | Requires a bow weapon |
| Minion / Abyssling / Rune Knight | Summoned entity type |
| Sentry | Deployed stationary attacker |
| Totem | Deployed stationary support structure |
| Trap | Placed triggered effect |
| Shout | Buff/debuff shout-type skill |
| Enhance (Attack/Defense) | Buff category |
| Seal | Sentence/seal-type activation |
| Weapon Range | Uses equipped weapon's attack range |

